           <a href="/about/docs/2019/NicholasChaseWinter2019.pdf">
            career information talk and Q &amp; A
           </a>
           session at 12:30 pm on Thursday, February 28th, 2019, in Jones 226. A pizza lunch will be provided.
          </p>
          <p class="stb">
           <strong>
            <a href="/about/docs/2019/2019_wtr_grads.pdf" target="_self" title="2019 Winter Graduates">
             Best Wishes to our Winter Quarter Graduates!
            </a>
